LOOP:
1. Listening (VAD on)
2. Speech ends â†’ process intent
3. If complex â†’ do web/vector lookup
4. Output response (TTS)
5. If user starts speaking mid-response:
     â†’ STOP speaking immediately
     â†’ Cancel TTS buffer
     â†’ Re-enter LISTENING mode
